<br>
<br>
~Sisters of Smyrna,<br>
       My tribe has gone to war against an evil known as the Saurians. They have attacked children attending XenaVerse High, they have attempted to conquer our Allies in Rome, they also have been killing the Ancient Tribe of the Odusians, Amazon Children of the Ancients. I seek assistance from my fellow sister tribes. This is a battle that will not be easilly won. Currently, they keep Eli of the Elisians captive, but I do not know how long they will allow him to live. Only come if you know you can be of service, I will not be responsible for the deaths of my athelfi. This is a greater enemy than the Centaurs ever could be. Come if you can to Scynthia.~<br>
<br>
          - Queen Alysia Lillian Loire -<br>
