<Young Amazon>"Queen Kala,we just got a message from Scynthia,I think you should see it."The young amazon could barely stay still for one second.<br>
Kala almost fell of the side of her bed as her door was nearly knocked off the hinges when the young amazon barged in.She sat up on her bed."Kelli,"She looked at the young amazon with anger."Don't you know how to knock?And settle down,you're making me dizzy."She didn't mean to sound too angry,but she did,the effects of 'expecting' seemed to be making her have mood swings.<br>
<Kelli>"My appologize,Queen Kala,but it's an urgent message from Scynthia!"<br>
"It's alright,Kelli."Kala got to her feet,and grabbed a long,heavy cloak from a hook on the wall,and swung it over her shoulders,then wrapping her arms tightly around herself."But please settle down,you wont make things any better if you can't calm down....Wheres the message?"Kala spoke as she made her way to the door of the hut.<br>
<Kelli>"This way..."And the young amazons leads Kala to the tree where the spear and message were.<br>
<br>
Upon reaching the tree,Kala noticed most of the amazons of Smyrna had already gathered around the tree to read the message.<br>
<Kelli>"Coming through!"She shouted as she lead Kala to the tree.<br>
A small pathway was then made for Kala to get to the tree and read the message.<br>
After reading the message,a grim look crosses Kalas features,she then turns to address her athelfi.<br>
<br>
"Sisters,listen.As many of you have read from this scroll,Scynthia,our allies,have gone to war,they need some help.Queen Alysia is a dear friend of mine,so i'm asking you all to pitch in and help.Their enemies sound like a tough bunch,So I am only asking those who have had the experience in fighting in war,to acctually go and fight,any others....stay clear of the battle,there will be injured that will need assistence off the battle grounds."She finished with that,and turned to head back to her hut to ready herself,she may be expecting,but if she could do anything to help her athelfi in Scynthia,you better damn well bet,she was going to do it. <p>|•| Kala of Smyrna |•|</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.showMessage?topicID=17.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.showMessage?topicID=15.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.emailToFriend?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.threadControl?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm16.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http:/